2017 is almost over, and the winter holidays are here once again. But this season isn’t just about celebrating with loved ones; it’s also about reliving years gone by.

At Backe, we wanted to take a trip back in time and share some of our favorite memories – of days when snow blanketed the ground and we spent hours making snow forts.

You can bring those moments back to life:

  • Select any of the drawings below by clicking on it.
  • Click on the colored marker you’d like to use, then apply it to the areas you want to color.
  • Save your completed drawing or print it out.
We look forward to seeing what you come up with! You can share your colorings with us by emailing them to info@backemarketing.com or through Facebook and Twitter.
Have a wonderful holiday season and a very happy new year!
